# Aggressive Scalper v1

This skill implements an aggressive scalping strategy optimized for 
volatile crypto markets. It uses RSI extremes as entry signals and 
maintains a strict 2:1 reward-to-risk ratio.

## Entry Criteria
- RSI < 30: Look for BUY opportunities
- RSI > 70: Look for SELL opportunities
- Confirm with volume (above 20-day average)

## Exit Criteria
- Stop Loss: 1% from entry
- Take Profit: 2% from entry

## Risk Management
- Maximum 2% of portfolio per trade
- No more than 3 concurrent positions
